<promed@promedmail.org>
[Although no human cases appear to have been linked to the
Salmonella-tainted sesame, ProMED has posted outbreaks related to
sesame seeds or products made from the seeds. - Mod.LL]
[One wonders about the origin of the sesame products used in the food
products that were associated with the outbreaks covered in the below
mentioned ProMED-mail postings. - Mod.MPP]
